610
00:39:08,554 --> 00:39:09,889
Sweetie Pie.

611
00:39:10,556 --> 00:39:12,391
That knife was heavier than I thought.

612
00:39:12,475 --> 00:39:14,018
It slipped off my hands.

613
00:39:16,645 --> 00:39:17,605
Let me do this.

614
00:39:18,606 --> 00:39:20,900
