won the bronze medal.

751
00:49:23,043 --> 00:49:25,921
Good work. Go to IBC
and send your manuscript to the editor.

752
00:49:26,004 --> 00:49:26,880
Yes.

753
00:49:26,963 --> 00:49:30,592
